Package org.jcvi.jillion.core.io

Utility package containing I/O related helper classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileVisitor
    FileVisitor is an base interface which uses the "push approach" to walk over complicated File structures.
    InputStreamSupplier
    A Supplier function that can create multiple new InputStreams from the same source file.
    TextFileVisitor
    TextFileVisitor is a FileVisitor that visits a text file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BufferSize
    Helper class to compute buffer sizes in bytes.
    FileUtil
    FileUtil is a Utility class containing common static methods to work with File objects.
    IOUtil
    IOUtil is a collection of static utility methods that make working with Input and Output easier.
    OutputStreams
    Helper method to create OutputStreams of various formats.
    PushBackBufferedReader
    A BufferedReader that allows lines to be pushed back to be read again.

Package org.jcvi.jillion.core.io Description

Utility package containing I/O related helper classes.
